Classes in com.alexgilleran.icesoap.request used by com.alexgilleran.icesoap.observer
Request
          Encapsulates all the code for making a SOAP Request - to use, create an object that implements the SOAPObserver class (generally this is easiest using anonymous objects from the activity or fragment) and attach it using the Request.registerObserver(SOAPObserver) method.

Classes in com.alexgilleran.icesoap.request used by com.alexgilleran.icesoap.request
ListRequest
           This request deals specifically with SOAP calls that recall a list of items, allowing listeners to be bound that will be called every time a new object is parsed rather than waiting until the entire request is finished.
